    "All methods in two environments are evaluated with the quit parameters: 𝑊 = 4, 𝛽 𝑆𝑡𝑒𝑎𝑚 = 50, and 𝛽 𝐴𝑚𝑎𝑧𝑜𝑛 = 15.",
    "The maximum round is set to 100.",
    "For all the RL-based methods, we leverage DeepFM [18] as the backbone following [15], and for all the LLM-based methods, we utilize the \"gpt-3.5-turbo-16k\" provided by OpenAI as the LLM backbone for its strong long context modeling ability.",
    "And the temperature is set to 0.5 for all experiments.",
